"iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1662,"height":933,"file_path":"/r7zUhTCs4QHvFHkF1HhhLUC0XQw.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.781,"vote_average":0},{"width":1660,"height":934,"file_path":"/rZZg4Fl6CCHq6yRsKQWfaPahjOw.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.777,"vote_average":0},{"width":1623,"height":913,"file_path":"/oyO0ijUcqQ6OVlG7xxRDWCusJew.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1653,"height":930,"file_path":"/2RpauCK5QMWWg7jAsdQEDcwqDy6.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.777,"vote_average":0},{"width":1657,"height":932,"file_path":"/qSydoQn7r1KyZ8VKEVpNTb4cKli.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1648,"height":927,"file_path":"/MM8aJcujfhIpZvwO0fgjdWoeKx.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1660,"height":934,"file_path":"/HYAK5e8abXcxzNkRURoh0AbxsV.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.777,"vote_average":0},{"width":1650,"height":928,"file_path":"/sCii8yPkhnK1hS0LOgKAxUykZaN.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1628,"height":916,"file_path":"/ckCXTjKg5EdXxQZpf4YMnhw9Y9T.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.777,"vote_average":0},{"width":1650,"height":928,"file_path":"/4Bx4d9JA6lqoKhbFXpRwCH14oo1.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/oRqpyT6lUKd8fPDP0R9J6jZGpJj.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/zpm66sbzYX3sShQTUqTpYQ0zUi.jpg","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/ir0qC0eSB0RCjayhkYdHgxLFtML.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":null,"enrichment_cycle":0,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"All About My Mother","runtime":101,"tagline":"Part of every woman is a mother/actress/saint/sinner. And part of every man is a woman.","homepage":"","overview":"Following the tragic death of her teenage son, Manuela travels from Madrid to Barcelona in an attempt to contact the long-estranged father the boy never knew. She reunites with an old friend, an outspoken transgender sex worker, and befriends a troubled actress and a pregnant, HIV-positive nun."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Alles über meine Mutter","runtime":105,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Pedro Almodóvar erzählt in diesem Film die Geschichte einer Frau, die auf der Suche nach dem Vater ihres verstorbenen Sohnes mit ihrer Vergangenheit konfrontiert wird."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Annem Hakkında Her Şey","runtime":101,"tagline":"Her kadının bir yanı anne/oyuncu/rahibe/günahkardır. Her erkeğin bir yanı ise kadındır.","homepage":"","overview":"Tek oğlu Esteban’ı yalnız başına büyüten ve ona çok bağlı olan Manuela, bir gece elim bir kazada oğlunu kaybeder. Duygusal bir çöküntü yaşayarak taşındığı Barcelona’da acısını indirmek için iş arayan Manuela, bir yandan da bir oğlu olduğundan habersiz eski kocasını aramaya başlar. Bu sırada eski dostu Agrado ve yeni tanıştığı Rosa ile sıkı bir dostluk kurup yeni bir hayata başlamaya çalışır. Ta ki trajedi kapısını yeniden çalana kadar…"},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Tutto su mia madre","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Manuela vive da sola con suo figlio adolescente Esteban che non ha mai conosciuto suo padre. Per il compleanno di Esteban Manuela lo porta a teatro dove si sta rappresentando \"Un tram chiamato desiderio\". I due sono uniti dall'ammirazione per l'attrice Huma Rojo e alla fine dello spettacolo per inseguire lei Esteban viene investito da una macchina. Manuela scappa da Madrid e va a Barcellona alla ricerca del padre di Esteban, che batte i marciapiedi con il nome di Lola."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Tout sur ma mère","runtime":101,"tagline":"Chaque femme est en partie mère, actrice, sainte, pécheresse. Et une partie de chaque homme est une femme.","homepage":"","overview":"Manuela, infirmière, vit seule avec son fils Esteban, passionné de littérature. Pour l'anniversaire de Manuela, Esteban l'invite au théâtre ou ils vont voir « Un tramway nommé désir ». À la sortie, Manuela raconte à son fils qu'elle a interprété cette pièce face à son père dans le rôle de Kowalsky. C'est la première fois qu'Esteban, bouleversé, entend parler de son père. C'est alors qu'il est renversé par une voiture. Folle de douleur, Manuela part à la recherche de l'homme qu'elle a aimé, le père de son fils."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Tudo Sobre a Minha Mãe","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Manuela perde o seu filho Esteban, de 18 anos, num acidente. A grande obsessão do rapaz consistia em saber quem era o seu pai, algo que ela sempre lhe tinha escondido. Em memória de Esteban, Manuela sente a necessidade de procurar o pai. Com esta intenção viaja para Barcelona, aonde se reencontra com o seu antigo amor, agora transformado numa mulher conhecida por Lola."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Vše o mé matce","runtime":101,"tagline":"Hledat muže jménem Lola není snadné...","homepage":"","overview":"Estéban tragicky zemřel. Bylo mu čerstvých sedmnáct a poslední řádky v jeho deníku patřily otci, se kterým se nikdy nesetkal, protože matku opustil dřív, než se o existenci svého syna stačil dozvědět. Estébanova matka se proto rozhodne vydat po stopách svého mládí, transvestitu Lolu najít a dodatečně ho spravit o jeho otcovství."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":101,"tagline":"Parte de cada mujer es madre/actriz/santa/pecadora. Y parte de cada hombre es una mujer.","homepage":"","overview":"Madrid. Manuela, una madre soltera, ve cómo su hijo muere el día en que cumple 17 años, por correr para conseguir el autógrafo de su actriz favorita. Decide entonces viajar a Barcelona en busca del padre de su hijo, un travestido llamado Lola, que ignoraba que tenía un hijo. Encuentra también a su amigo Agrado, otro travesti, y a través de él conoce a Rosa, una monja española y, por pura casualidad, Manuela termina convirtiéndose en la asistente de Huma Rojo, la actriz que admiraba su hijo."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Wszystko o mojej matce","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://gutekfilm.pl/wszystko-o-mojej-matce-almodovar","overview":"\"Wszystko o mojej matce\"  Pedro Almodóvar'a opowiada historię kobiety, która musi zmierzyć się z własną przeszłością i stara się odnaleźć ojca swojego syna. Ten hołd oddany matce skusił do kin dwa miliony Hiszpanów."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Све о мојој мајци","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Мануелин син гине желећи да добије аутограм познате глумице. Премда га је одгајила без мужа, и он је притом био њено једино дете, њена туга је неизрецива. Убрзо после сахране одлази у Барселону да потражи његовог оца, трансвестита Лолу, међутим налази његовог пријатеља који је упознаје са Розом, младом опатицом и социјалном радницом. Роза има веома лош однос са својим родитељима, а када затрудни све постаје још горе, те тражи помоћ од Мануеле. Ова у међувремену улази у траг глумици због које је њен син погинуо и њих две постају пријатељице..."},"name":"Srpski","iso_639_1":"sr","iso_3166_1":"RS","english_name":"Serbian"},{"data":{"title":"关于我母亲的一切","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"这部荣获奥斯卡奖的剧情片，作为佩德罗·阿尔莫多瓦尔最受喜爱的作品之一，以令人目眩神迷的动人笔触，探索了母性的深刻内涵。护士玛努埃拉（塞西莉亚·罗特 饰）在瞬间失去了她独自抚养成人的少年儿子。满怀悲恸的她前往巴塞罗那寻找孩子失联多年的父亲，在那里她于一个由特殊成员组成的家庭中重获新生——这个家庭包括一位感染艾滋病毒的怀孕修女（佩内洛普·克鲁兹 饰）、一位辉煌的戏剧明星（玛丽莎·帕雷德斯 饰），以及一位跨性别性工作者（安东尼娅·圣胡安 饰）。影片演绎精湛，处处闪耀着对电影艺术的致敬，既是对女性坚韧精神的礼赞，亦是一幅独一无二的家庭群像，更是一部充满无边人文关怀的杰作。[标准收藏]"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Всё о моей матери","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"На мать-одиночку Мануэлу обрушивается самое ужасное из земных несчастий — в автокатастрофе погибает её единственный сын Эстебан. Подвергнувшись спонтанному порыву, убитая горем женщина возвращается в город своей бурной юности — Барселону. Там она встречается с призраком Прошлого, чьи уродливые когти безжалостно царапают судьбы людей в Настоящем. Мануэле предстоит встреча с отцом Эстебана и его окружением, от которых она сбежала шестнадцать лет назад."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Wanneer Manuela haar 17-jarige zoon Esteban verliest bij een auto-ongeluk reist ze af naar Barcelona om zijn vader het droevige nieuws te vertellen. Esteban's vader gaat tegenwoordig als vrouw door het leven en heeft nooit van het bestaan van zijn zoon geweten."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Mindent anyámról","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Egy görög mondás szerint csak azok a nők látnak tisztán, akiknek könny áztatta a szemét. Manuelára nem igaz ez a mondás. Azon az estén, mikor egy autó halálra gázolja Estebant, a fiát, Manuela minden könnyét kisírja. S ahelyett, hogy tisztábban látna, a jelen és a jövő teljesen összekuszálódik benne. Fia egy hátrahagyott naplójában az alábbiakat olvassa: \"Tegnap anyám egy fényképet mutatott nekem. A fele hiányzott. Úgy érzem, az életemből is hiányzik ez a rész.\" Az apjáról volt szó. Manuela sosem beszélt róla fiának, nehéz lett volna megmagyarázni, hogy a férfinek nagyobb mellei vannak mint neki és hogy Lolának hívják. A hallgatás mint egy szörnyű bűn, úgy nehezedik vállaira. Elhatározza, hogy megkeresi Lolát, hogy elmondja neki, volt egy fiuk, aki már halott."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Όλα για τη μητέρα μου","runtime":101,"tagline":"Μέρος κάθε γυναίκας είναι μια μητέρα/ηθοποιός/αγία/αμαρτωλή. Και μέρος κάθε άντρα είναι μία γυναίκα.","homepage":"","overview":"Όταν χάνει τον 17άχρονο γιο της σε αυτοκινητιστικό δυστύχημα, η μητέρα του πάει στη Βαρκελώνη για να βρει τον πατέρα του. Χώρισαν πριν γεννηθεί το παιδί γιατί εκείνος έγινε τραβεστί. Κατά την διάρκεια της αναζήτησης, η γυναίκα, συναντά μια καλόγρια με AIDS και μια σταρ του θεάτρου."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"הכל אודות אמא","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"אימרה יוונית גורסת כי רק נשים שעיניהן נשטפו בדמעות, ראייתן צלולה. אצל מנואלה זה לא בדיוק עובד. בלילה שבו התבשרה על מות בנה בכתה עד שיבשו עיניה, אבל חייה מעולם לא נראו כל כך אפלים וקודרים. באותו לילה נוראי בביה\"ח קראה את המשפט האחרון שכתב בנה ביומנו ובו מובעים געגועים לדמות אב. וכך, לזכר פרי בטנה, היא עוזבת את מדריד ויוצאת לברצלונה בחיפוש אחר הגבר שאותו עזבה לפני כמעט 18 שנה וכרסה בין שיניה. היא רוצה לספר לו על התיסכול שטרד את בנם המנוח לפני שנהרג, על כך שקראה לו אסטבן על שמו - ז\"א עד שהחליף האב את שמו ללולה..."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"내 어머니의 모든 것","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"간호사인 마누엘라는 문학을 좋아하는 아들 에스테반과 단둘이서 산다. 마누엘라의 생일을 맞이해서 에스테반은 엄마에게 연극 <욕망이라는 이름의 전차>를 보여주는데, 연극이 마친 후 마뉴엘라는 에스테반에게 스탠리역을 했던 에스테반의 아빠와 이 연극을 공연했다는 이야기를 한다. 아빠에 대한 이야기를 처음 들은 에스테반은 아빠를 보고 싶어하는데..."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Tudo Sobre Minha Mãe","runtime":101,"tagline":"Uma homenagem às mulheres que atuam, às mulheres que sofrem e às mulheres que amam.","homepage":"","overview":"Após a morte de seu amado filho adolescente em um acidente, Roth deixa Madri para Barcelona para lidar com sua dor, ficar com velhos amigos e – talvez – entrar em contato com o pai – distante – que o menino nunca conheceu."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Alt om min mor","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Manuela mister sin søn Esteban i en tragisk trafikulykke. Sønderknust tager hun til Barcelona for at fortælle Estebans far – den transkønnede Lola – den frygtelige nyhed. Og gøre et gammelt regnskab op."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"オール・アバウト・マイ・マザー","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"マドリードに住む移植コーディネーターのマヌエラは、作家志望の息子・エステバンを女手一つで育ててきた。エステバンの誕生日、二人は『欲望という名の電車』の舞台を観に行く。そして、マヌエラが息子に今まで話さなかった父のことを話そうと決心したとき、エステバンは舞台の主演だった大女優ウマ・ロッホにサインをもらおうとして車にはねられ、そのまま亡くなってしまう。  息子の死を行方不明となっている父に伝えるため、バルセロナへ旅立ったマヌエラは、ひょんなことから息子の死の原因となったウマの付き人になる。バルセロナでマヌエラは、ウマのレズビアンの恋人で麻薬中毒の若手女優・ニナ、性転換した明るいゲイの娼婦・アグラード、エイズを抱えて妊娠した純朴なシスター・ロサ、その母親でボケの進んだ夫に手を焼く厳格な贋作画家、そして、今では「ロラ」という名の女性となりロサにエイズをうつした、息子と同名の元夫といった様々な女性たちと出会い、やがて人生への希望を取り戻していく。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Allt om min mamma","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Manuela är sjuksköterska och ensamstående mor till tonårssonen Esteban. De har det bra tillsammans och det enda Esteban saknar är att veta vem hans far är, men om detta är hans mamma förtegen. Mor och son delar intresset för film och teater. På väg hemifrån en teaterföreställning rusar Esteban fram till en av skådespelarna för att få en autograf och blir då överkörd av en bil och dör. Manuela börjar nu leta efter Estebans pappa för att berätta vad som hänt."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Всичко за майка ми","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Младият Естебан мечтае за две неща - да стане известен писател и да открие баща си, когото майка му Мануела умело прикрива."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"Všetko o mojej matke","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Esteban tragicky zomrel. Mal čerstvých sedemnásť a posledné riadky v jeho denníku patrili otcovi, s ktorým sa nikdy nestretol, pretože matku opustil skôr, než sa o existencii svojho syna stačil dozvedieť. Estébanova matka sa preto rozhodne vydať po stopách svojej mladosti"},"name":"Slovenčina","iso_639_1":"sk","iso_3166_1":"SK","english_name":"Slovak"},{"data":{"title":"我的母親","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"有一句古老的希臘諺語說，女人只能用淚水洗滌過雙眼，才能更看得清楚世事。這句諺語，對馬努薇拉而言卻未必是真。那夜，她的兒子艾斯提本車禍身亡，馬努薇拉獨坐在醫院長廊，痛哭至淚水流盡，徹底乾涸。但是她眼前的未來，卻仍然晦暗不明，馬努薇拉望著兒子的屍體，任憑她的回憶與現實，相互交織消失於黑暗裡．．．  清晨，她仍待在醫院裡遲遲不忍離去。打開兒子隨身攜帶的筆記本，發現筆記本上最後一頁寫著『．．有天早晨，我偷偷進了母親臥室，突然發現一疊被剪成一半的照片，照片上被剪去的那一半，我想應該是我的父親。看不到他，一股非常強烈的感覺向我襲來──我的人生有缺憾，就如照片失去的那一半！我渴望可見到我的父親，我不在意他是誰，或者他曾對母親做過什麼。沒有人！沒有人能剝奪我對他的這種感覺。』馬努薇拉從未曾告訴艾斯提本，他的父親是怎麼樣的人，當艾斯提本問起，她總是說：『你父親在你出生前就死了。』她是如此不願去回憶往事，但是為了她死去的兒子，馬努薇拉決定離開馬德里，到巴塞隆納尋找艾斯提本的父親。 她想要告訴艾斯提本的父親，即使他們的兒子從未見過這個父親，但是艾斯提本生前所寫下的話語，卻充滿了對父親的想像與渴望。也是因為兒子的遺願，才能驅使她再度前去尋找他。  當與艾斯提本的父親重逢時，馬努薇拉想告訴他，十八年前當她離開他時，她已經有了身孕，之後她為他們生下一個兒子，他可以是稱職的父親。但是如今已經沒了機會，因為他們的兒子，在不久之前因為車禍身亡了。馬努薇拉還想告訴他，他們的兒子叫做艾斯提本，正如他的生身父親一樣，但是那個英俊的艾斯提本如今已經改名叫做蘿拉！  馬努薇拉就這樣去了巴賽隆納，尋找兒子的父親──蘿拉，要尋找擁有這樣名字的『男人』，本來就是一件很詭異的事，而這一段為兒尋父的路途，竟也開啟了一段令人匪夷所思的旅程．．．．"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Все про мою матір","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Мануела працює в клініці з трансплантації органів в Мадриді. Вона живе зі своїм 17-річним сином Естебаном. Трохи замкнутий у собі Естебан захоплюється віршами і старими фільмами. Але головний об'єкт його інтересу, постійних досліджень та аналізу — це минуле його матері і як наслідок доля батька, якого він ніколи не знав. Він починає писати сценарій під назвою «Все про мою матір»."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"Todo sobre mi madre","runtime":105,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Una madre soltera en Madrid ve morir a su único hijo en su cumpleaños mientras corre a buscar el autógrafo de una actriz. Junto a ella con pena, regresa a Barcelona para contarle al padre del niño sobre la muerte del hijo que nunca supo que tenía."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Totul despre mama mea","runtime":101,"tagline":"O parte din fiecare femeie este o mamă/actriță/sfântă/păcătosă. Și o parte din fiecare bărbat este o femeie.","homepage":"","overview":"În urma morții tragice a fiului ei adolescent, Manuela călătorește de la Madrid la Barcelona în încercarea de a-l contacta pe tatăl înstrăinat de mult pe care băiatul nu l-a cunoscut niciodată. Ea se reîntâlnește cu o veche prietenă, o lucrătoare sexuală transgender și se împrietenește cu o actriță cu probleme și cu o călugăriță însărcinată, seropozitivă."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"論盡我阿媽","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"為償亡兒遺願，單親媽媽重回舊地訪尋「他變她」的孩子生父，遇上被虐待的變性舊友、被同性伴侶背叛的女伶，還有被「她」弄至懷孕兼感染愛滋病的修女，冥冥中重拾母親角色。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"ყველაფერი დედაჩემის შესახებ","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ერთადერთი შვილის დაღუპვის შემდეგ მარტოხელა დედა ბარსელონაში მიემგზავრება, რათა მოძებნოს ბავშვის მამა, რომელმაც არაფერი იცოდა მისი არსებობის შესახებ."},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"Vse o moji materi","runtime":97,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Manuela se po smrti 17-letnega sina Estebana, ki ga je od rojstva vzgajala kot samohranilka, preseli v Barcelono, kjer namerava poiskati sinovega odtujenega očeta. Ta se je vmes preimenoval v Lolo in je zdaj ženska. Manuela v novem mestu spozna pisano družbo novih prijateljic, ki so si v oporo v težkih časih. Spoprijatelji se s staro znanko, transspolno prostitutko Agrado, z redovnico Roso, ki nosi Lolinega otroka in je HIV-pozitivna, z gledališko divo Humo Rojo, ki igra Blanche Dubois v predstavi Tramvaj poželenje, in z zasvojenko Nino Cruz, Humino soigralko in ljubimko. Manuela se noče posloviti od materinske vloge in posvoji Rosinega otroka."},"name":"Slovenščina","iso_639_1":"sl","iso_3166_1":"SI","english_name":"Slovenian"},{"data":{"title":"关于我母亲的一切","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"玛努埃拉 的丈夫在儿子出生前就离开了妻子，玛努埃拉成为了单身妈妈，带着儿子埃斯特班来到马德里生活。儿子从不知道爸爸的事情，玛努埃拉只好对儿子说父亲已经过世。然而，儿子终究不相信。他在日记本里悄悄写下对父亲的想念。车祸来得那么突然，儿子被一辆迎面撞来的汽车夺走了生命。母亲悲伤不已，决定去找孩子的父亲洛拉，完成儿子心愿。然而她却得知，洛拉已经换装成女人，当了妓女，而且染上了艾滋病。更不幸的是，修女罗萨 怀上了洛拉的孩子。玛努埃拉留在罗萨身边照顾她，罗萨诞下的婴儿也取自己儿子埃斯特班的名字，苦难的日子终于有了希望--这个新生儿竟然逃过了艾滋的噩运。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"SG","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Wanneer Manuela haar 17-jarige zoon Esteban verliest bij een auto-ongeluk reist ze af naar Barcelona om zijn vader het droevige nieuws te vertellen. Esteban's vader gaat tegenwoordig als vrouw door het leven en heeft nooit van het bestaan van zijn zoon geweten."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"BE","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Alles über meine Mutter","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nach dem plötzlichen Tod ihres Sohnes fährt Manuela nach Barcelona – jene Stadt, die sie vor 18 Jahren unglücklich verlassen hat. Dort begibt sie sich auf die Suche nach dem Kindsvater, der mittlerweile Frauenkleider trägt und sich Lola nennt. Konfrontiert mit Erinnerungen und alten Sehnsüchten, findet sie sich bald in einem Strudel der Ereignisse wieder, an deren Ende ein Neubeginn steht …"},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"AT","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Alles über meine Mutter","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Die trauernde Mutter Manuela reist nach dem Unfalltod ihres 17-jährigen Sohnes Esteban nach Barcelona, um dessen letzten Wunsch zu erfüllen: Seinen leiblichen Vater zu finden. Obwohl sie weiß, dass sie sich bei ihrer Suche mit ihrer Vergangenheit konfrontiert wird, vor der sie 17 Jahre zuvor geflohen ist, verliert sie keine Zeit. Manuela weiß genau wo sie suchen muss: Auf dem Straßenstrich. Dort trifft sie nicht nur den Vater von Esteban, der mittlerweile auf den Namen Lola hört und Frauenkleider trägt, sondern auch ihre alte Freundin Agrado. Über sie lernt sie Rosa kennen, eine Schwester, die sich für Prostituierte einsetzt, die ein schlimmeres Schicksal auf ihren Schultern tragen müssen. Manuela beginnt sich um Rose, die mit HIV infiziert ist und ein Kind erwartet, sowie die anderen Frauen zu kümmern..."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"CH","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Kaikki äidistäni","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Kaikki äidistäni kertoo äidistä, joka näkee 17-vuotiaan poikansa kuolevan etsiessään suurta idoliaan: näyttelijätär Humaa. Merkillisten tapahtumien seurauksena hänestä tulee Human henkilökohtainen assistentti."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"Alt om min mor","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"\"Alt om min mor\" kretser rundt en mor som ser sin 17-årige sønn dø i jakten på sitt store idol; skuespillerinnen Huma. Gjennom en rekke merkelige hendelser ender hun opp som Humas personlige assistent."},"name":"Bokmål","iso_639_1":"nb","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian Bokmål"},{"data":{"title":"Alt om min mor","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"\"Alt om min mor\" kretser rundt en mor som ser sin 17-årige sønn dø i jakten på sitt store idol; skuespillerinnen Huma. Gjennom en rekke merkelige hendelser ender hun opp som Humas personlige assistent."},"name":"Norsk","iso_639_1":"no","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian"},{"data":{"title":"Alt om min mor","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"\"Alt om min mor\" kretser rundt en mor som ser sin 17-årige sønn dø i jakten på sitt store idol; skuespillerinnen Huma. Gjennom en rekke merkelige hendelser ender hun opp som Humas personlige assistent."},"name":"","iso_639_1":"nn","iso_3166_1":"NN","english_name":"Norwegian Nynorsk"},{"data":{"title":"Kõik minu emast","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Üksikema Manuela kaotab ootamatult oma teismelise poja Estebani. Oma leina leevendamiseks otsustab ta reisida Barcelonasse, et otsida üles Estebani isa, kes ei ole teadlik poja olemasolust. Tema tragikoomiline rännak viib ta kokku mitmete omamoodi naistega, kellede hulka kuuluvad näiteks transsooline prostituut Agrado ja rase nunn Rosa."},"name":"Eesti","iso_639_1":"et","iso_3166_1":"EE","english_name":"Estonian"},{"data":{"title":"Viss par manu māti","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Latviešu","iso_639_1":"lv","iso_3166_1":"LV","english_name":"Latvian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"58cba3d1c3a368288900d872","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/58cba3d1c3a368288900d872","author":"lmao7","content":"This film got my attention right away because of the references to 2 of my fave old Hollywood films : All About Eve and Streetcar Named Desire. Melodramatic with a lil comedy. My fave scene when all 4 ladies were at the couch just chatting and laughing. I love all the characters (maybe not Nina). Agrado…for the win! Penelope…what a beautiful nun, so sad about her situation though. Huma, at first kinda off (as she didn’t give the autograph to the son) but as the movie went on, I liked her character more and more. And Cecilia, very empowering. At first, the other characters were supposed to be helping the mother but in the end, she was the one who helped all of them, in a way. Feel good dramatic film.","created_at":"2017-03-17T08:52:33.559Z","updated_at":"2021-06-23T15:57:55.850Z","author_details":{"name":"lmao7","rating":8,"username":"lmao7","avatar_path":"/ekmYOUU4tfx9zGGadjRdE7UPce.jpg"}},{"id":"62c99851498bc20698a14f2e","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/62c99851498bc20698a14f2e","author":"badelf","content":"Of course, it's an Almodovar, so it's already a great film. But this one - the artistic shots, the characters, the story, the humanity - all top notch. I think this film might be his best.","created_at":"2022-07-09T15:01:37.352Z","updated_at":"2022-07-09T15:01:37.352Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":10,"username":"badelf","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"6800e415aacf7cfb269a2752","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/6800e415aacf7cfb269a2752","author":"CinemaSerf","content":"$11","created_at":"2025-04-17T11:20:54.141Z","updated_at":"2025-04-17T11:23:28.044Z","author_details":{"name":"CinemaSerf","rating":7,"username":"Geronimo1967","avatar_path":"/9HcQx0Yfbxy8eqr3ft66X9uWMf0.jpg"}},{"id":"6800e41383c6e567c7d984b7","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/6800e41383c6e567c7d984b7","author":"CinemaSerf","content":"$12","created_at":"2025-04-17T11:21:03.098Z","updated_at":"2025-04-17T11:22:24.686Z","author_details":{"name":"CinemaSerf","rating":7,"username":"Geronimo1967","avatar_path":"/9HcQx0Yfbxy8eqr3ft66X9uWMf0.jpg"}}],"recommendations":[{"id":64,"adult":false,"title":"Talk to Her","video":false,"overview":"Two men share an odd friendship while they care for two women who are both in deep comas.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2588,"vote_count":1407,"poster_path":"/fWDbQlOWOqjR5jZm98KjGyYmUOw.jpg","release_date":"2002-03-15","vote_average":7.58,"backdrop_path":"/9aCRXFWT1rd1nZDcEtWILKb2Sap.jpg","original_title":"Hable con ella","original_language":"es"},{"id":140,"adult":false,"title":"Bad Education","video":false,"overview":"When an old friend brings filmmaker Enrique Goded a semi-autobiographical script chronicling their adolescence, Enrique is forced to relive his youth spent at a Catholic boarding school.","genre_ids":[18,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3992,"vote_count":1038,"poster_path":"/du716YH0PKiL2kZgIPLkEblgHLX.jpg","release_date":"2004-03-19","vote_average":7.362,"backdrop_path":"/wNFiDhGnrnSfyqYxzeAa8mFnUhj.jpg","original_title":"La mala educación","original_language":"es"},{"id":8223,"adult":false,"title":"Kika","video":false,"overview":"When American author Nicholas brings in a cosmetologist named Kika to prepare the corpse of his recently deceased son, she inadvertently revives the young man, then falls in love with him. Forces conspire against the couple, though, as Nicholas wants Kika for himself.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.3881,"vote_count":311,"poster_path":"/jUEBKaMqcvrz0HHF8Cei8asjRWr.jpg","release_date":"1993-10-29","vote_average":6.399,"backdrop_path":"/l8dbS5uLR2IzRu3qwMOXCUBRLnh.jpg","original_title":"Kika","original_language":"es"},{"id":219,"adult":false,"title":"Volver","video":false,"overview":"Three generations of women survive the east wind, fire, insanity, superstition and even death by means of goodness, lies and boundless vitality.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3876,"vote_count":1866,"poster_path":"/m1ZUDGTFtVGE3zjTvF8OiQ9um5e.jpg","release_date":"2006-03-17","vote_average":7.469,"backdrop_path":"/cLvcOx8RbSUPCbkynKzNIg1zc2g.jpg","original_title":"Volver","original_language":"es"},{"id":267,"adult":false,"title":"Live Flesh","video":false,"overview":"When Victor attempts to seduce Elena, all he gets for his trouble is a one-way, six-year ticket to prison, where he concentrates on strengthening his mind, his body... and his desire for vengeance on the man who put him there. After his release and still madly in love with her, Victor will stop at nothing to win her over even if means revenge, for Elena has married David, the cop who sent him to prison!","genre_ids":[18,10749,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3088,"vote_count":723,"poster_path":"/7YPGYeamF6AuyxhKqbd5oNKKCCy.jpg","release_date":"1997-10-10","vote_average":7.041,"backdrop_path":"/tR5JCOmayMV7Ml2ycA7NQ5E8Xyo.jpg","original_title":"Carne trémula","original_language":"es"},{"id":8088,"adult":false,"title":"Broken Embraces","video":false,"overview":"Harry Caine, a blind writer, reaches this moment in time when he has to heal his wounds from 14 years back. He was then still known by his real name, Mateo Blanco, and directing his last movie.","genre_ids":[18,10749,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3284,"vote_count":700,"poster_path":"/uPTOKnc9bzPp1emH3TyuKOGIylQ.jpg","release_date":"2009-03-18","vote_average":7.147,"backdrop_path":"/shrpF5ZivObmV3hnCK8sSS0DP5z.jpg","original_title":"Los abrazos rotos","original_language":"es"},{"id":4203,"adult":false,"title":"Women on the Verge of a Nervous Breakdown","video":false,"overview":"After being dumped by her lover, Pepa finds her life and the lives of those around her spiraling out of control in a deliciously chaotic series of events.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.4707,"vote_count":978,"poster_path":"/8C5FJlUo96pj1xAs2BKnB58PYzi.jpg","release_date":"1988-03-25","vote_average":7.412,"backdrop_path":"/eRzwmzyz4sSq2QqjXWehWNkU0Us.jpg","original_title":"Mujeres al borde de un ataque de nervios","original_language":"es"},{"id":442811,"adult":false,"title":"Sunday's Illness","video":false,"overview":"Annabel is a successful businesswoman with a wealthy husband. At a reception in her villa she meets a woman, a member of the catering staff who has been hired for the evening. This woman is none other than her own daughter Chiara, whom she had left over thirty years ago. Chiara was just eight years old at the time. She now approaches her mother with an unusual request: to spend ten days together with her.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2575,"vote_count":111,"poster_path":"/AqSYUeWKo7CfJqJh8uIzpeTuXqo.jpg","release_date":"2018-02-23","vote_average":6.617,"backdrop_path":"/yhp0XL2qzloIXMELePuGgkbinIT.jpg","original_title":"La enfermedad del domingo","original_language":"es"},{"id":741770,"adult":false,"title":"My Fat Arse and I","video":false,"overview":"One morning, a girl tries on a pair of new pants, but they won’t zip up. In the mirror she sees herself as the fattest piglet the world has ever seen. To change this, she decides to go on a strict diet. Hunger quickly turns her into a kind of zombie, stumbling blindly to the fridge that seems to haunt her at night. In one of those moments, the Angel of the United Bitches of Slimbuttlandia appears, carrying a royal invitation to visit the kingdom and take part in a mysterious royal ceremony.","genre_ids":[16],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0804,"vote_count":26,"poster_path":"/jaGrOBWYsiA5JczJUPuTxWTTXXt.jpg","release_date":"2020-05-12","vote_average":6.692,"backdrop_path":"/mUP9eS0sL4SYRNNkUgsQsRb6MNH.jpg","original_title":"Ja i moja gruba dupa","original_language":"pl"},{"id":55,"adult":false,"title":"Amores Perros","video":false,"overview":"A fatalistic car crash in Mexico city sets off a chain of events in the lives of three people: a supermodel, a young man wanting to run off with his sister-in-law, and a homeless man.","genre_ids":[18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.1714,"vote_count":2847,"poster_path":"/A4lH22nlFF7MdalGfcvSrlC1ttt.jpg","release_date":"2000-06-16","vote_average":7.633,"backdrop_path":"/nFXBmQAjNGdQUFPdTxE1OFqjx0X.jpg","original_title":"Amores perros","original_language":"es"},{"id":144789,"adult":false,"title":"I'm So Excited!","video":false,"overview":"Something has gone wrong with the landing gear of a plane en route from Madrid to Mexico City. The group of eccentric travelers on the flight, defenseless in the face of danger, indulge in colourful confessionals, while the outlandish crew attempts to find ways to entertain them.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6436,"vote_count":707,"poster_path":"/sQSHPwWlqW9AJEac6sakeIhrMZx.jpg","release_date":"2013-03-08","vote_average":5.708,"backdrop_path":"/EccrWxeF28GeGLSSuDOU9suom5.jpg","original_title":"Los amantes pasajeros","original_language":"es"},{"id":4593,"adult":false,"title":"The Discreet Charm of the Bourgeoisie","video":false,"overview":"In Luis Buñuel’s deliciously satiric masterpiece, an upper-class sextet sits down to dinner but never eats, their attempts continually thwarted by a vaudevillian mixture of events both actual and imagined.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.7482,"vote_count":887,"poster_path":"/zN4ILX2x64PvT2jIOAHXxCOi5WA.jpg","release_date":"1972-09-15","vote_average":7.461,"backdrop_path":"/z6NI6n5MvQZMZJbXKLiyFl1yDeA.jpg","original_title":"Le Charme discret de la bourgeoisie","original_language":"fr"},{"id":146,"adult":false,"title":"Crouching Tiger, Hidden Dragon","video":false,"overview":"Two warriors in pursuit of a stolen sword and a notorious fugitive are led to an impetuous, physically-skilled, teenage nobleman's daughter, who is at a crossroads in her life.","genre_ids":[12,18,28,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.9682,"vote_count":3481,"poster_path":"/iNDVBFNz4XyYzM9Lwip6atSTFqf.jpg","release_date":"2000-07-06","vote_average":7.434,"backdrop_path":"/nSm9cij9VRrGDoZoS16CPnX0FqK.jpg","original_title":"卧虎藏龍","original_language":"zh"},{"id":2469,"adult":false,"title":"Tie Me Up! Tie Me Down!","video":false,"overview":"After being released from a mental hospital, a troubled young man tracks down an actress he once had sex with and forces her into captivity, determined to make her part of his life.","genre_ids":[35,10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.176,"vote_count":677,"poster_path":"/4eNyqA543ixNCME8pcADgP9wb1i.jpg","release_date":"1990-01-22","vote_average":6.833,"backdrop_path":"/ovxdPoXYb3raXOAqokCqkCR83Jx.jpg","original_title":"¡Átame!","original_language":"es"},{"id":1391,"adult":false,"title":"Y Tu Mamá También","video":false,"overview":"In Mexico, two teenage boys and an attractive older woman embark on a road trip and learn a thing or two about life, friendship, sex, and each other.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.3722,"vote_count":1696,"poster_path":"/aj3rqjab8jfc2fWmcS3H3c5qbur.jpg","release_date":"2001-06-08","vote_average":7.417,"backdrop_path":"/7aW9IZjpsoTXYEARlnOvTtl6EBr.jpg","original_title":"Y tu mamá también","original_language":"es"},{"id":63311,"adult":false,"title":"The Skin I Live In","video":false,"overview":"A brilliant plastic surgeon creates a synthetic skin that withstands any kind of damage. His guinea pig: a mysterious and volatile woman who holds the key to his obsession.","genre_ids":[18,27,9648,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.2301,"vote_count":4547,"poster_path":"/xa7uCwGYykrf8MMI8iF5dZvNlrG.jpg","release_date":"2011-08-17","vote_average":7.49,"backdrop_path":"/qn8NzshtQmJD7Nm06sAp5yOtexH.jpg","original_title":"La piel que habito","original_language":"es"},{"id":52109,"adult":false,"title":"Love Streams","video":false,"overview":"Two closely-bound, emotionally wounded siblings reunite after years apart.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5961,"vote_count":142,"poster_path":"/c5uyQfWvzCVsCHL13J5JBZ61SQJ.jpg","release_date":"1984-03-22","vote_average":7.2,"backdrop_path":"/gxo0Tw1MUy2eo3s1VLfdN5ebt8G.jpg","original_title":"Love Streams","original_language":"en"},{"id":443486,"adult":false,"title":"Red Istanbul","video":false,"overview":"Orhan who lived in London for years and did not come back to Turkey agrees to help Deniz -a famous director- edit his first book. Deniz has been living in a mansion with his family which started to lose its old brightness and power. Orhan finds himself in the middle of Deniz's complicated relationships, mysterious friends and stange family members. This is the first movie of Ferzan Ozpetek which is shot in Turkey after a long time. It is also based on his own book which has the same name with the movie.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.933,"vote_count":138,"poster_path":"/nSzgyCPVJVVKtb7LhvRoEjnyaQP.jpg","release_date":"2017-03-02","vote_average":5.696,"backdrop_path":"/qa2Oonwq1hNews3snq0aWgL0w24.jpg","original_title":"İstanbul Kırmızısı","original_language":"tr"},{"id":51940,"adult":false,"title":"Happy New Year, Charlie Brown","video":false,"overview":"It's the night of Peppermint Patty’s New Year’s Eve bash, but Charlie Brown has to write a book report about War and Peace. Hoping to join the fun for a special dance with the Little Red-Haired Girl, he tries desperately to finish in time.","genre_ids":[10751,16,35,10770],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4951,"vote_count":65,"poster_path":"/bzkOg991CsVIakFmqSxUhQq2UbY.jpg","release_date":"1986-01-01","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/gmujbMGy9G6OTzjcjZegyGId10W.jpg","original_title":"Happy New Year, Charlie Brown","original_language":"en"},{"id":187028,"adult":false,"title":"Omar","video":false,"overview":"The drama, the story of three childhood friends and a young woman who are torn apart in their fight for freedom, is billed as the first fully-financed film to come out of the Palestinian cinema industry.","genre_ids":[53,18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0186,"vote_count":180,"poster_path":"/mzCdtXQYdLPrNr16Ld5ZowavKoa.jpg","release_date":"2013-05-21","vote_average":7.056,"backdrop_path":"/16CMTxHLSTAIIQPsJQQigXuNxFc.jpg","original_title":"عمر","original_language":"ar"}],"similar_content":[{"id":463005,"adult":false,"title":"Moreno","video":false,"overview":"When Chris arrives at the village of T'boli in lake Sebu, South Cotabato, he thought he has left his dark recent past behind. He is working on commission as a video documentarist to make a profile on the women T'boli and their changing views on multiple marriages. The most affluent men, called Datu, marry more than once and each time pays dowry to the family of the women they marry. When a young T'boli woman, Ngapon, tells Chris that she wants to be free from a marriage that was set by her parents and to go to Manila, Chris begins to confront waht he left in the city. Like the proud Datu with many wives, Chris has Denver, a bronze skinned lover in Manila, who is proud of his relationships. Denver lives with Chris in an apartment as partners yet he still goes into sexual and emotional relationships with other men. Ngapon's quest for freedom becomes Chris journey to a very sad dark past.  - Written by Anonymous","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.245,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":"/oKRDC0ul0qXzaLBeis8k2aHSKTl.jpg","release_date":"2007-06-20","vote_average":4.1,"backdrop_path":"/tmULj2zOy644sKW4yayc1fqimYX.jpg","original_title":"Moreno","original_language":"tl"},{"id":93,"adult":false,"title":"Anatomy of a Murder","video":false,"overview":"Semi-retired Michigan lawyer Paul Biegler takes the case of Army Lt. Manion, who murdered a local innkeeper after his wife claimed that he raped her. Over the course of an extensive trial, Biegler parries with District Attorney Lodwick and out-of-town prosecutor Claude Dancer to set his client free, but his case rests on the victim's mysterious business partner, who's hiding a dark secret.","genre_ids":[80,18,9648],"popularity":2.1998,"vote_count":1125,"poster_path":"/b2G1QSAwtBv9luhEwErIgSRaU92.jpg","release_date":"1959-07-01","vote_average":7.836,"backdrop_path":"/xfEU7DOlQPwz8Y0TBhKmpETuNIc.jpg","original_title":"Anatomy of a Murder","original_language":"en"},{"id":108,"adult":false,"title":"Three Colors: Blue","video":false,"overview":"The wife of a famous composer survives a car accident that kills her husband and daughter. Now alone, she shakes off her old identity and explores her newfound freedom but finds that she is unbreakably bound to other humans, including her husband’s mistress, whose existence she never suspected.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":3.0844,"vote_count":1849,"poster_path":"/33wsWxzsNstI8N7dvuwzFmj1qBd.jpg","release_date":"1993-09-08","vote_average":7.64,"backdrop_path":"/nAyUVvcdOKHmukdgGHZ7xR5er1q.jpg","original_title":"Trois couleurs : Bleu","original_language":"fr"},{"id":110,"adult":false,"title":"Three Colors: Red","video":false,"overview":"Part-time model Valentine unexpectedly befriends a retired judge after she runs over his dog. At first, the grumpy man shows no concern about the dog, and Valentine decides to keep it. But the two form a bond when she returns to his house and catches him listening to his neighbors’ phone calls.","genre_ids":[18,9648,10749],"popularity":2.3485,"vote_count":1520,"poster_path":"/JHmsBiX1tjCKqAul1lzC20WcAW.jpg","release_date":"1994-05-12","vote_average":7.905,"backdrop_path":"/pZcoSJUb3Lgr9Rzg2shg1PtTBP9.jpg","original_title":"Trois couleurs : Rouge","original_language":"fr"},{"id":116,"adult":false,"title":"Match Point","video":false,"overview":"Chris, a former tennis pro, takes a job as an instructor and befriends his wealthy young student, Tom. After being introduced to his family, Chris is soon engaged to Tom's sister, Chloe. Despite the professional and financial advantages that this relationship affords him, Chris becomes obsessed with Tom's fiancee, American actress Nola.","genre_ids":[18,10749,53],"popularity":3.2355,"vote_count":4297,"poster_path":"/vHjEVTD8ucuwKSFOZJeyAnTZYli.jpg","release_date":"2005-10-26","vote_average":7.4,"backdrop_path":"/yUJf20GQ5vifhk9QDxUGotAEaLz.jpg","original_title":"Match Point","original_language":"en"},{"id":15,"adult":false,"title":"Citizen Kane","video":false,"overview":"Newspaper magnate Charles Foster Kane is taken from his mother as a boy and made the ward of a rich industrialist. As a result, every well-meaning, tyrannical or self-destructive move he makes for the rest of his life appears in some way to be a reaction to that deeply wounding event.","genre_ids":[9648,18],"popularity":6.0189,"vote_count":5936,"poster_path":"/sav0jxhqiH0bPr2vZFU0Kjt2nZL.jpg","release_date":"1941-04-17","vote_average":7.98,"backdrop_path":"/9Y85oA1y6toL2OACXdaC6iTl7eQ.jpg","original_title":"Citizen Kane","original_language":"en"},{"id":1252309,"adult":false,"title":"Tell Me What You Want","video":false,"overview":"After his father's death, Eric Zimmerman travels to Spain to oversee his company's branches. In Madrid, he falls for Judith and engage in an intense, erotic relationship full of exploration. However, Eric fears his secret may end their affair.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"popularity":12.7566,"vote_count":268,"poster_path":"/yZXYCiZQPB7Ui6D5206W1zDKv8P.jpg","release_date":"2024-11-29","vote_average":6.131,"backdrop_path":"/8Rseq6hAhAItnTrbECEFt35VoSJ.jpg","original_title":"Pídeme lo que quieras","original_language":"es"},{"id":26,"adult":false,"title":"Walk on Water","video":false,"overview":"Eyal, an Israeli Mossad agent, is given the mission to track down and kill the very old Alfred Himmelman, an ex-Nazi officer, who might still be alive. Pretending to be a tourist guide, he befriends his grandson Axel, in Israel to visit his sister Pia. The two men set out on a tour of the country, during which Axel challenges Eyal's values.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.7146,"vote_count":91,"poster_path":"/mVWFN3RaBFLuJRtRLPebatX9qPq.jpg","release_date":"2004-02-05","vote_average":6.835,"backdrop_path":"/z5YFbE9VVHwDXbXbqZdoO6THqPs.jpg","original_title":"ללכת על המים","original_language":"he"},{"id":28,"adult":false,"title":"Apocalypse Now","video":false,"overview":"At the height of the Vietnam war, Captain Benjamin Willard is sent on a dangerous mission that, officially, \"does not exist, nor will it ever exist.\" His goal is to locate - and eliminate - a mysterious Green Beret Colonel named Walter Kurtz, who has been leading his personal army on illegal guerrilla missions into enemy territory.","genre_ids":[18,10752],"popularity":12.0335,"vote_count":8894,"poster_path":"/gQB8Y5RCMkv2zwzFHbUJX3kAhvA.jpg","release_date":"1979-05-19","vote_average":8.267,"backdrop_path":"/eN5G8vTWLnZxJ0LTd4g27oPObcZ.jpg","original_title":"Apocalypse Now","original_language":"en"},{"id":55,"adult":false,"title":"Amores Perros","video":false,"overview":"A fatalistic car crash in Mexico city sets off a chain of events in the lives of three people: a supermodel, a young man wanting to run off with his sister-in-law, and a homeless man.","genre_ids":[18,53],"popularity":5.1714,"vote_count":2847,"poster_path":"/A4lH22nlFF7MdalGfcvSrlC1ttt.jpg","release_date":"2000-06-16","vote_average":7.633,"backdrop_path":"/nFXBmQAjNGdQUFPdTxE1OFqjx0X.jpg","original_title":"Amores perros","original_language":"es"},{"id":64,"adult":false,"title":"Talk to Her","video":false,"overview":"Two men share an odd friendship while they care for two women who are both in deep comas.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":1.2588,"vote_count":1407,"poster_path":"/fWDbQlOWOqjR5jZm98KjGyYmUOw.jpg","release_date":"2002-03-15","vote_average":7.58,"backdrop_path":"/9aCRXFWT1rd1nZDcEtWILKb2Sap.jpg","original_title":"Hable con ella","original_language":"es"},{"id":462698,"adult":false,"title":"Fantasy of the Girls","video":false,"overview":"Upon helping her friend audition for their all-girls high school's production of Romeo & Juliet, freshman Sun-wha is unexpectedly cast as Juliet. To her surprise Romeo is played by the über-cool and stunning senior Ha-nam, whom all the girls seem to have a crush on. As the two would-be thespians grow closer, Ha-nam takes Sun-wha under her wing in more ways than one. However this sparks the jealousy of the play's director, Su-yeon, whom, it turns out, is more than friends with Ha-nam.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.7446,"vote_count":23,"poster_path":"/am7C4K6cWMhfqmkEsOvXUg0zFpo.jpg","release_date":"2018-11-29","vote_average":5.7,"backdrop_path":"/2gUxTdEMkJk4RYWunh9ggcPAFgp.jpg","original_title":"소녀의 세계","original_language":"ko"},{"id":1058128,"adult":false,"title":"The Astronaut Lovers","video":false,"overview":"Pedro travels from Spain to Argentina for a vacation at his uncle's home, where he meets Maxi again, a childhood friend. Maxi is surprised when he finds out Pedro is gay. When Maxi finds his ex-girlfriend is also there, he asks Pedro to pretend to be his boyfriend to win her back. Pedro accepts the game, unaware of the dangers of playing with love.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":1.1756,"vote_count":56,"poster_path":"/hyu2nt255VLL4RgGCAtcDK8RLv3.jpg","release_date":"2024-06-20","vote_average":8.214,"backdrop_path":"/9unmtNASKsj8OmPWQ2VQCcCWF00.jpg","original_title":"Los amantes astronautas","original_language":"es"},{"id":653594,"adult":false,"title":"I Carry You with Me","video":false,"overview":"An epic love story spanning decades is sparked by a chance encounter between two men in provincial Mexico. Based on a true story, ambition and societal pressure propel an aspiring chef to leave his soulmate and make the treacherous journey to New York, where life will never be the same.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.3327,"vote_count":64,"poster_path":"/yI3XakDqPSElfJACmk3mYnrPn78.jpg","release_date":"2021-06-25","vote_average":7.1,"backdrop_path":"/pEaswlPhx6ocV5w0J6lpNBs2GjO.jpg","original_title":"Te llevo conmigo","original_language":"es"},{"id":653788,"adult":false,"title":"The Glider","video":false,"overview":"Bruno pursues Fabrice, runs without calculation, to fly away with him, until the end.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.1574,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/lycfra6ce82Q7MK6dsN8CR1uCQk.jpg","release_date":"1999-12-01","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/zd0IGRDZiUuJSZQzP46kGEJbEU2.jpg","original_title":"Le planeur","original_language":"fr"},{"id":68,"adult":false,"title":"Brazil","video":false,"overview":"Low-level bureaucrat Sam Lowry escapes the monotony of his day-to-day life through a recurring daydream of himself as a virtuous hero saving a beautiful damsel. Investigating a case that led to the wrongful arrest and eventual death of an innocent man instead of wanted terrorist Harry Tuttle, he meets the woman from his daydream, and in trying to help her gets caught in a web of mistaken identities, mindless bureaucracy and lies.","genre_ids":[35,878],"popularity":3.6643,"vote_count":3611,"poster_path":"/aewan59WcFThBimkTVVoNf2o5Vb.jpg","release_date":"1985-02-20","vote_average":7.666,"backdrop_path":"/9IYyCLf5NNAQFK9pNtqzEU9HWzM.jpg","original_title":"Brazil","original_language":"en"},{"id":71,"adult":false,"title":"Billy Elliot","video":false,"overview":"County Durham, England, 1984. The miners' strike has started and the police have started coming up from Bethnal Green, starting a class war with the lower classes suffering. Caught in the middle of the conflict is 11-year old Billy Elliot, who, after leaving his boxing club for the day, stumbles upon a ballet class and finds out that he's naturally talented. He practices with his teacher Mrs. Wilkinson for an upcoming audition in Newcastle-upon Tyne for the royal Ballet school in London.","genre_ids":[18,35,10402],"popularity":2.4028,"vote_count":4026,"poster_path":"/nOr5diUZxphmAD3li9aiILyI28F.jpg","release_date":"2000-09-28","vote_average":7.593,"backdrop_path":"/mTsbahr4SLqgVZkKRN0O8t5iA9y.jpg","original_title":"Billy Elliot","original_language":"en"},{"id":76,"adult":false,"title":"Before Sunrise","video":false,"overview":"An unexpected meeting on a train leads two travelers to spend an evening wandering through Vienna. As the night unfolds, they share stories and conversations about life and love, exploring new ideas while a quiet intimacy grows between them, knowing it may be their only night together.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":4.8061,"vote_count":4566,"poster_path":"/kf1Jb1c2JAOqjuzA3H4oDM263uB.jpg","release_date":"1995-01-27","vote_average":7.972,"backdrop_path":"/qA2TyqPldTtoTVY3LKrNIG5g6bH.jpg","original_title":"Before Sunrise","original_language":"en"},{"id":80,"adult":false,"title":"Before Sunset","video":false,"overview":"Nine years later, Jesse travels across Europe giving readings from a book he wrote about the night he spent in Vienna with Celine. After his reading in Paris, Celine finds him, and they spend part of the day together before Jesse has to again leave for a flight. They are both in relationships now, and Jesse has a son, but as their strong feelings for each other start to return, both confess a longing for more.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":3.0312,"vote_count":3709,"poster_path":"/4sW5XH9ZfYXpvFzev00S1IGAEbg.jpg","release_date":"2004-06-16","vote_average":7.809,"backdrop_path":"/tcZi0LQc5iu2u6i5aOWyj9NBBvl.jpg","original_title":"Before Sunset","original_language":"en"},{"id":271388,"adult":false,"title":"Velociraptor","video":false,"overview":"During the end of the world, two best friends walk around their city, talking about their sex lives, and one of them reveals they are still a virgin.","genre_ids":[35,18,14],"popularity":0.2151,"vote_count":19,"poster_path":"/mGuQBdevB7q2JK6PMqYjCVrXN8W.jpg","release_date":"2014-06-07","vote_average":5.132,"backdrop_path":"/6feb1sjJdNvXQJXw9n6G07SZIR3.jpg","original_title":"Velociraptor","original_language":"es"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt0185125","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q329805","instagram_id":null},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":148154,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":n